Moore 11 (Darnell L. Moore &amp;#34;On Location: The &amp;#34;I&amp;#34; in the Intersection&amp;#34; December 12, 2011, http://thefeministwire.com/12011/12/on-location-the-%E2%80%9Ci%E2%80%9D-in-the-intersection/ MA in Theology from Princeton, Fellow at NYU LGBT/ Feminism Dpt., past Adjunct at Rutgers-Newark, Member of the Newark LGBTQ Commission

&amp;#34;The most general statement of our politics... we would need to start at a different location that we might&amp;#39;ve expected: self.&amp;#34;</headline></objectSummary></objects>